alia'''{{Flagicon|Australia}} \n*[[Adam Gilchrist]], [[Daniel Christian]], [[Mitchell Marsh]], [[Ryan Harris (cricketer)|Ryan Harris]], [[Daniel Harris (cricketer)|Daniel Harris]], [[Chris Lynn]], [[Andrew Symonds]], [[Cameron White]]\n'''South Africa'''{{Flagicon|South Africa}}\n*[[Herschelle Gibbs]], [[Juan Theron]], [[JP Duminy]]\n'''Pakistan'''{{Flagicon|Pakistan}} \n*[[Shahid Afridi]]\n'''Sri Lanka'''{{Flagicon|Sri Lanka}} \n*[[Kumar Sangakkara]], [[Nuwan Zoysa]], [[Chaminda Vaas]], [[Chamara Silva]]\n'''New Zealand'''{{Flagicon|New Zealand}} \n*[[Scott Styris]]\n'''England'''{{Flagicon|England}} \n*[[Michael Lumb (cricketer)|Michael Lumb]]\n'''West Indies'''{{Flagicon|West Indies}} \n*[[Dwayne Smith]], [[Fidel Edwards]], [[Kemar Roach]]\n\n==Results==\n===Overall results===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Summary of results\n|-\n! !! Played !! Wins !! Losses !! Tied !! Win % !! Position\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align: center; \"| '''IPL'''\n|-\n! [[IPL 2008|2008]]\n| 14 || 2 || 12 ||0 || 14% || 8/8\n|-\n! [[IPL 2009|2009]]\n| 16 || 9 || 7|| 0 || 56% || 1/8\n|-\n! [[IPL 2010|2010]]\n| 16 || 8 || 8 || 0 || 50% || 4/8\n|-\n! [[IPL 2011|2011]]\n| 14 || 6 || 8 || 0 || 42% || 7/10\n|-\n! [[IPL 2012|2012]]\n| 15 || 4 || 11 || 0 || 26.67% || 8/9\n|-\n! Total\n| '''75''' || '''29''' || '''46''' ||'''0''' || '''38.67%'''\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align: center; \"| '''Champions League T20'''\n|-\n! [[2009 Champions League Twenty20|2009]]\n| 2 || 0 || 2|| 0 || 0% || 10/12\n|-\n! Total\n| '''2''' || '''0''' || '''2''' || '''0''' || '''0%''' || ''' '''\n|-\n! colspan=\"7\" style=\"text-align: center; \"| '''Overall'''\n|-\n! Overall\n| '''77''' || '''29''' || '''48''' || '''0''' || '''37.67%''' || ''' '''\n|}\n\n==Awards, records and statistics==\n\n===Awards===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Award !! Player !! Year !! Achievement\n|-\n| Player of the Tournament || [[Adam Gilchrist]] || 2009 || 495 Runs and 15 dismissals\n|-\n| Under-23 Success of the Tourname